<H2>Recommendations/Suggestions Window</H2>
<P>This Window allows you to add any recommendations or suggestions from the Packages currently selected
for intallation to the Package Configuration Window.</P>
<P>It is reached from the "View..." button on the Package Configuration Window.</P>
<P>It checks all the packages selected for installation or upgrade and any recommendations or suggestion
that are not already selected for installation or have already been installed and shows them in this
window with a check box beside them.</P>
<P>Check the option button for the packages you would like to be added to the installation.</P>
<P>The window contains the following buttons</P>
<ul>
<li>Add selected - Adds the selected packages to the Package Configuration Window.</li>
<li>Cancel - Close the window without adding any Packages to the installation.</li>
</ul>
</BODY>
